[API] Added an example for deleting all index templates

    curl -XDELETE localhost:9250/_template/*
    {"acknowledged":true}

[API] Removed the `indices_boost` from the list of method arguments

Prefer `indices_boost` as a part of the DSL:

```ruby
client.search(
  index: 'articles,comments',
  body: {
    query: { query_string: {query: 'foo'} }
    indices_boost: {'articles' => 5, 'comments' => 1}
  }
)
```

Thanks @jarib!

Closes #29

[CLIENT] Added "retry on failure" and "reload on failure" features

Example:

@client = Elasticsearch::Client::Client.new %w| localhost:9250 foobar1 foobar2 foobar3 |,
                                          retry_on_failure: 1000

@client = Elasticsearch::Client::Client.new %w| localhost:9250 foobar1 foobar2 |,
                                          reload_on_failure: true
